Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right! I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:56.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay! Hurry back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And don't forget\nthe ninja treats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:02.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you see Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:06.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha left on Kirara\nearly in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.16,0:02:09.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think he went quite far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:12.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... there's one place\NI can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:14.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:18.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The only one who knows\NTetsusaiga's true power
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is the one who forged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:22.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean, Old Totosai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He really intends to\nbreak through Naraku's barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To that old man's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:48.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:51.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You would know a way to\nbreak through any barrier...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,however strong it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However strong, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not like there isn't a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or that there is a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:03.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:07.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have to get stronger when\NNaraku's out of commission!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, it itches!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:14.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.\NI haven't bathed in a week.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:19.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Totosai! I doubt he's gonna\ntell me so easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:23.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to be patient and\ncoax it outta him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:25.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:30.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh... it itches!\NMy back, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai! I know it's difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I need you to teach me\nhow to break the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:38.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boy, I need... I need a bath!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:41.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there some way\NI can train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:45.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A bath... in order to\nget a bath ready...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I have to get the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get water?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's so hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:56.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To haul enough water from the river\nat the bottom of the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:57.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to fill the tub.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:01.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then cut all the wood out back\ninto firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such humbug.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:07.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Getting a bath for one as old as I\n{\i1}is such a chore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:09.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cutting wood?\NIs that training?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:10.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Training?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:11.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:12.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, you're here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master, I will {\i1}not{\i0}\ngo away today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who's this fox demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wrong! I'm a Lynx Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:26.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've asked Master Totosai\nto train me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:27.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Train?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:32.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want Master Totosai to train me\nso I can break the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:34.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm itchy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can use them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ahem! You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:46.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want you to fetch some water\nand cut some wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it!\NThat's special training!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:50.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fetching water builds up\nessential muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And cutting wood improves\nyour fighting posture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And heating the bath water\nbuilds up your lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Every task has a meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:04.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa told me that's been the\ntradition on the continent
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:05.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,for four thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.64,0:05:06.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:10.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're willing to teach me\nhow to break the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, l just wanted to...\NTake a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:15.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Totosai, I guess\nyou need strength
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to learn this special\ntechnique, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, then.\NI'll stay and train.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been staying in that hut\nover yonder for ten days!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm the senior apprentice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Senior apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:32.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:34.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In the human world, there's an\napprenticeship system!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:37.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The one who came first\nis the senior apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't dawdle and follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:45.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry! Junior apprentice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:48.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're under the wrong\nimpression...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I think I'm going to\nget my bath.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I left without saying a word\nto Kagome and the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's gonna take more time\nthan I expected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:18.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Meow!\NThat's impossible for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not "Meow"! I'm Bunza!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay then, Bunza.\NDon't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:27.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna train harder\nthan you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:30.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and have the Master teach\nme the method first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:32.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you need to learn\nthe method so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:40.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:49.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey lemme go!\NI said lemme go, Junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:52.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't training!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:54.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lemme go!\NJust lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said don't overdo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:08.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I must learn the technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's not training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! You're such a handful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:44.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:54.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? You haven't even eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:04.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you've stayed here in this\nhut for ten days?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:07.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No wonder you got sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:12.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I m-must train and learn\nthe technique to break the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First, get well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bring you something\ngood to eat later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why are you so kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:29.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... there's a kid about your age\namong my companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe someone's gossiping\nabout you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is great for\nbuilding up the lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:56.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... such a nice bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:01.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Tell me if there's any\nother way to train!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:05.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll do anything if it's to\nmaster the technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Train?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:09.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:13.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it true that you're making\NInuyasha train?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:17.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, actually...\NI wanted to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:20.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When one is old, fetching water\nis so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:24.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When I mentioned it, before I knew it,\nhe decided it was training!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's{\i0} the one who jumped to\nthe wrong conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:30.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've never seen Inuyasha\nlooking so earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he learns the truth,\NI fear what will happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:40.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}All you wanted was bath water?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How frightening!\NIt's making me shiver with fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... I'm getting chicken skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:50.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NI came to wash your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you're cold, I'd better\nburn more wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:11.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here, have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:13.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're sick.\NDon't question!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:16.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you want to train?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:28.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, you don't have to\ntalk if you don't feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:38.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon named Nanafushi took\nover the mountain where we,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Lynx Demon tribe, lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:42.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And he built a barrier around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:46.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We weren't able to go into the\nmountain, couldn't gather food...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,our entire lives were disrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:52.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,According to Pa,\nwho's the tribe leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:56.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,only Totosai can make a weapon\nthat would break the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:00.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Totosai would know\na special technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Totosai is an old eccentric,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:06.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who refuses to teach\njust anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:10.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The members of the tribe are beginning\nto turn their backs on Pa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I'm so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:17.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want everyone to recognize\NPa as their leader once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:24.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For Pa's sake, I must learn\nand master the technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:29.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Torako!\NIs that you, Torako?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:38.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why've you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:44.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong, Bunza?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:46.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa went to get Nanafushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:51.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He went inside the barrier\nto take back the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,even if he doesn't know\nthe technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:57.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bunza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa! Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:23.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NI sensed something just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:25.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?\NSensed something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:29.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Did Bunza come\nthis way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:33.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, that may've been\NBunza just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Which way'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:35.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Atta way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Bunza!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not itchy at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it this way, Torako?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:02.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bunza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:15.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bunza!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:19.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll go together!\NI'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:28.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's my Pa!\NI'll rescue him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with you.\NYou're under no obligation to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:40.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't you say we were\nbrother apprentices?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The senior apprentice\nand the junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't that connection enough\nto help?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, ain't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:14.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your Pa's inside the barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:23.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But how'd he get inside\nthe barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:32.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nanafushi opened the barrier\nso he could kill Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:48.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa knew it was a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still, in order to save\nthe others...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:58.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He chose to fight as the leader\nof the Lynx tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:03.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.90,0:15:08.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's my father! It's a son's duty\nto save his father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:10.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I'm coming along as\nyour junior!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:12.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That okay, senior?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:15.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah... Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:42.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your father's okay. We made it\nin time to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:44.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:15:59.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:03.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It didn't work at all.\NI'm no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:10.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your attack has Nanafushi scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:23.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.20,0:16:43.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit hiding and\ncome on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:53.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright... perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:06.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Taking up the safe spot\nall for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:07.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was a short time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:23.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I'll see what my training\nwith Totosai yields.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My training with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although it was for\njust a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:31.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'll put it all\ninto this sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do it, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:34.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:42.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind... Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:01.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:06.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh-oh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:32.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:33.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:42.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:05.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:10.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It... it was Master Totosai's\ntraining, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:17.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I kinda feel like I'm stronger\nthan before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keep up with your training!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:28.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:32.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You've saved your Pa. Now train\nto become the leader of your tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll meet again, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:35.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:43.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come see us... Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Inuyasha? Where've you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... just out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:56.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But listen, your training worked.\NI'm stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:57.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:02.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry... I made you do those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:03.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:07.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... It's hard to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:09.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you mistakenly thought that\nyou would become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if you had gone in search\nof Naraku's barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you may've been in\ngrave danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:17.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:22.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, there's no way you've\ngotten stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Then the training?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:29.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l just wanted to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:30.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:34.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, yes! You jumped to\nconclusions yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:39.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. You see, I haven't\nbathed in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:39.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:41.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:45.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no technique to break\NNaraku's barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's not as though\nthere isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it's not as though\nthere is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:57.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:01.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was just going to tell him!\NHe's so rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:06.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, he had labored\nhard and persevered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought I'd teach him\nthe method
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to become stronger to enable\nhim to break the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it THAT method?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:17.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Can you tell\NInuyasha about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:19.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:21.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:24.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be thankful you ended up\nwith just one lump on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:29.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was away a whole night\nwithout telling them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:32.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess everyone's worried.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:37.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm back.\NSorry I worried you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ninja food is always\nso delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.06,0:21:43.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This flavor, we just can't\nduplicate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:46.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You weren't here,\nso I ate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:50.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!\NThat's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:52.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:54.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:58.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cripes! I brought you\nspecial treats.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.95,0:22:00.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's your fault for\nnot being here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:03.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!\NCan't you be more concerned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:07.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so hopeless.\NI'll share just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:08.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.39,0:23:52.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It controls the seas and\nhunts down humans and demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:53.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the Demon Bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.53,0:23:55.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes... and if he destroys it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:58.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga will gain the power\nto break the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:23:59.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But there's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:04.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A half-demon, one just like\NMaster Inuyasha, protects the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:08.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But she's a girl... so I don't know if\NInuyasha can willingly kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.31,0:24:12.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Shiori's Family and {\i1}Inuyasha's{\i0} Feelings"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,0:24:14.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aah, a bath feels nice after all...
